description.en: Baby Floki Coin is Elon Musk’s very own shiba inu and he’s on a mission to become the first puppy to go to the moon! He’s built to reward you by sending 5% of every transaction made to your wallet. This little guy loves space exploration- simply hold, and watch your $BabyFlokiCoin go to the moon!
